* Wed Apr 11 2001 fforest
  - API change display_itemlist so if the flags parm is 0
    we dont display the Action title and the MOD,DEL,VIEW options.
    so we can use it for nice tableized reports also.
  - lib/module_billing change ShowBillsToMark to optionally display
    the preview box as opposed to displaying it all the time
  - reports.php needed the filename suffix added to 'new module_list() function
  - mcsi_nsf* modules can now generate a link to the file created for 
    submission so the user can left click to download. this makes it easier
    to get the file till mcsi allows us to interface. This also requires a
    alias line in httpd.conf Alias /tmp /bills no <Directory> option is
    required or recommened.
  - unpaid_procs report module somehow lost its alternate color stuff.

